OL,3,CPublic first look inside multi-million
OL,4,Cpound Rochdale Town Hall transformation
OL,6,FVisitors have been taking a look
OL,7,Faround one of the most historic
OL,8,Fbuildings in the North West after a
OL,9,Fmulti-million pound restoration.
OL,11,FThe doors have reopened at the Grade I
OL,12,FListed Rochdale Town Hall after work
OL,13,Fcosting #20 million, with a #8.9
OL,14,Fmillion grant from the National
OL,15,FLottery Heritage Fund.
OL,17,FOpened in 1871, the town hall is one
OL,18,Fof the finest Victorian buildings of
OL,19,Fits kind in the country.
