OL,6,FThe town's newly elected MP George
OL,7,FGalloway was at the opening and said
OL,8,Fthe building was a "jewel" and part of
OL,9,Fthe plan to make "Rochdale great
OL,10,Fagain".
OL,12,FThe council building has been closed
OL,13,Fsince 2020 and will now operate as a
OL,14,Ftourist attraction for the first time
OL,15,Fin its 153 year history.
OL,17,FThe scheme has restored many of the
OL,18,Fbuilding's historic features and
OL,19,Fcreated new community spaces in rooms,
OL,20,Fwhich were previously out of bounds to
OL,21,Fthe public.
