OL,6,FTeams of specialists, and more than
OL,7,F500 volunteers, have spent 4 years
OL,8,Ftransforming the space and restoring
OL,9,Fit to its former glory.
OL,11,FA number of the building's historic
OL,12,Ffeatures include decorative ceiling
OL,13,Fpanels and angels in the Great Hall,
OL,14,Fthe Magna Carta mural, the extensive
OL,15,Fstained glass, painted surfaces and
OL,16,Fstonework have been painstakingly
OL,17,Frestored and cleaned.
