OL,6,FSome of the most dramatic changes have
OL,7,Ftaken place in the Great Hall, where
OL,8,Fspecialists used a variety of
OL,9,Fequipment, including cotton wool buds,
OL,10,Fto restore the 350 panels which cover
OL,11,Fthe room's ceiling.
OL,13,FA visitor from Tunisia was asked for
OL,14,Fher first impressions.
OL,16,F"It's amazing. It's my first time
OL,17,Fbeing here, and I was, like,
OL,18,Fastonished of what I'm seeing right
OL,19,Fnow."
