OL,6,FShe chatted to a local resident who
OL,7,Fwas thrilled by the transformation.
OL,9,F"I remember how it was. And so this is
OL,10,Fso different. And yet I'm so proud of
OL,11,Fwhat we've achieved."
OL,13,FYears of grime had to be removed to
OL,14,Freveal some of the building's
OL,15,Fintricate details, including English
OL,16,Flions and Scottish thistle, which can
OL,17,Fbe viewed for the first time in
OL,18,Fdecades.
