OL,6,FThe Exchange and Grand staircase was
OL,7,Fbuilt to allow people to exchange
OL,8,Fcotton goods and is the main entrance
OL,9,Fto the building.
OL,11,FThe marble pillars and dramatic stone
OL,12,Fvaulted ceiling have been cleaned to
OL,13,Fcreate a lighter space.
OL,15,FA permanent exhibition space, known as
OL,16,Fthe Welcome Gallery, tells the story
OL,17,Fof Rochdale, its people and its past.
