OL,6,FThe first visitors were treated to the
OL,7,Fsounds of the Rochdale Music Service
OL,8,FFanfare, and the Bombay Raja brass
OL,9,Fband will bring Bollywood music to the
OL,10,Fevent.
OL,12,FCouncillor Neil Emmott, leader of the
OL,13,Fcouncil, said: "It's been a long wait
OL,14,Ffor our residents and I'm delighted
OL,15,Fthat they will finally get to see
OL,16,Ftheir beautiful town hall, fully
OL,17,Frestored in all its glory."
