OL,6,F"Rochdale Town Hall is probably one of
OL,7,Fthe finest examples of neo gothic
OL,8,Farchitecture in the country, but like
OL,9,Fmany buildings this old, it was
OL,10,Fshowing its age.
OL,12,F"Now, after four years of painstaking
OL,13,Fwork, it looks incredible, just as it
OL,14,Fwould have done when it first opened
OL,15,Fits doors well over a century ago."
